reviews.text: We passed by a restaurant - putien, a Chinese style food, it looks spacious which is good for our dinner time. Mum  Was caught by the red mushroom card on the table. Noticed that it well-known in China, thus we ordered it without hesitation. The food and soup is high recommended which is really out of expectation. Soup is sooo sweet and no chicken powder at all , haha.
Light flavours. Nice food.
Yummy foods and friendly staffs
Tasty and good spacing for dinning in Hong Kong nowaday. Also will provide kids meal free of charge. Love it!
Dedicated dishes with Chinese and western culture

result.name: 莆田

reviews.text: 好味😋
老實講呀， 就算我真係執到錢呀我都唔會去莆田食， 我相信啲餸菜， 是最細碟的一間， 再唔會搵到第二間咁細碟㗎啦。
荃灣廣場“莆田”主打福州菜比較地道口味，帶有新加玻漁民風格！味道偏向淡香風味，令人回味，感慨。。。
公司由於在莆田附近，所以也會偶爾來吃吃莆田，小妹最愛吃海鮮，知道蟶子又回來了，所以和同事一起來吃吃，$198 2款，有8款選擇，我地揀左幾道蟶子菜式試試，特別推薦鐵板鹽焗蟶子跟新菜品叄芭炒蟶子，鐵板吃到原味，加上花椒，沾上一點鹽更加能帶出蟶子鮮味，而叄芭醬是星馬特式醬料，加上韭菜花一起炒，非常香口，推介這個蟶子。👍👍

reviews.text: Good shopping mall with a slightly upscale tint to it. Has nice open areas throughout and several floors to explore. Additionally, it does have several styles of cuisine and snacks on location, which makes it very good for just casual hanging out if you're in Tsuen Wan.
Shopping mall with a good variety of shops and restaurants, playground area good for kids.
Shop and restuarant are so great but car parking is poor

medium sized shopping centre but there are a number of this type of shopping centres that are connected by flyovers here. hence, it is a part of a huge shopping complex in the area. recommended if you would like to spend an afternoon here. you never run out of shopping options.
mon to fri parking reasonable
